06:50:20.450 --> 06:50:21.990
He can be compared to the sun

7143
06:50:21.990 --> 06:50:23.450
that shines for all of us.

7144
06:50:23.970 --> 06:50:26.610
In different languages of the world

7145
06:50:26.610 --> 06:50:28.390
it can be called differently.

7146
06:50:28.390 --> 06:50:33.050
This is Surya, Sun, Sun, Sol, Shams.

7147
06:50:33.710 --> 06:50:35.710
But it doesn't change

7148
06:50:35.710 --> 06:50:38.410
its qualities and shines for all of us,

7149
06:50:38.870 --> 06:50:40.130
and it makes us happy.

7150
06:50:40.590 --> 06:50:43.370
Just like God has different names,

7151
06:50:44.470 --> 06:50:46.190
we can call him Allah,

7152
06:50:46.410 --> 06:50:47.650
we can call him Krishna,

7153
06:50:48.090 --> 06:50:50.330
God, Allah, God,

7154
06:50:50.790 --> 06:50:52.310
and many, many other names.

7155
06:50:52.850 --> 06:50:54.170
But he is one.

7156
06:50:54.590 --> 06:50:56.930
And this can be compared

7157
06:50:56.930 --> 06:50:57.570
with the sun.

7158
06:51:03.130 --> 06:51:03.750
You know,

7159
06:51:03.870 --> 06:51:05.630
different religions and teachings

7160
06:51:05.630 --> 06:51:07.650
are like rays

7161
06:51:07.650 --> 06:51:09.270
that come from the sun.

7162
06:51:09.590 --> 06:51:11.250
After all, it is God who has sent us

7163
06:51:11.250 --> 06:51:13.370
all the religions and teachings

7164
06:51:13.370 --> 06:51:14.370
along with the prophets.

7165
06:51:14.670 --> 06:51:18.490
They all come from one source.

7166
06:51:18.790 --> 06:51:21.850
In the Bhagavad Gita,

7167
06:51:21.930 --> 06:51:23.350
in chapter 4,

7168
06:51:23.470 --> 06:51:24.790
verse 7-8,

7169
06:51:24.970 --> 06:51:26.090
verse 7-8,

7170
06:51:26.090 --> 06:51:28.670
Lord Krishna addresses Arjuna,

7171
06:51:28.770 --> 06:51:31.230
every time when a religion falls

7172
06:51:31.230 --> 06:51:33.190
and becomes devoid of God,

7173
06:51:33.270 --> 06:51:35.450
I myself descend into this world

7174
06:51:35.450 --> 06:51:37.010
in search of the Bharata

7175
06:51:37.010 --> 06:51:38.350
to free the righteous

7176
06:51:38.350 --> 06:51:39.870
and destroy the villains,

7177
06:51:40.070 --> 06:51:43.330
as well as to restore the empty religion.

7178
06:51:43.810 --> 06:51:46.790
I come there from age to age.

7179
06:51:48.250 --> 06:51:49.610
I Myself appear

7180
06:51:49.610 --> 06:51:52.570
millennium after millennium.

7181
06:51:52.690 --> 06:51:56.070
So, friends, let's preach to each other

7182
06:51:56.070 --> 06:51:58.110
the common human values

7183
06:51:58.110 --> 06:52:00.490
that God and His prophets have bequeathed,

7184
06:52:00.510 --> 06:52:01.630
such as love,

7185
06:52:01.890 --> 06:52:02.430
respect,

7186
06:52:02.730 --> 06:52:03.170
friendship,

7187
06:52:03.970 --> 06:52:04.590
honesty.

7188
06:52:06.130 --> 06:52:06.950
The main thing is love,

7189
06:52:07.050 --> 06:52:08.630
because God is love.

7190
06:52:09.030 --> 06:52:11.050
In chapter 8,

7191
06:52:12.490 --> 06:52:14.170
verse 28, it says,

7192
06:52:14.550 --> 06:52:15.790
a person who has entered

7193
06:52:15.790 --> 06:52:17.490
the path of faithful service

7194
06:52:17.490 --> 06:52:19.150
is not deprived of the blessings

7195
06:52:19.150 --> 06:52:21.310
that are achieved by studying the Vedas,

7196
06:52:21.470 --> 06:52:22.310
by asceticism,

7197
06:52:22.470 --> 06:52:23.290
by making sacrifices,

7198
06:52:24.030 --> 06:52:25.110
by giving alms,

7199
06:52:25.110 --> 06:52:26.910
by doing philosophical research

7200
06:52:26.910 --> 06:52:30.110
and pious karmic activity.

7201
06:52:30.250 --> 06:52:32.530
Simply by serving the Lord,

7202
06:52:32.710 --> 06:52:34.190
he gains the fruits

7203
06:52:34.190 --> 06:52:36.330
of all these types of activities

7204
06:52:36.330 --> 06:52:37.690
and at the end of his life

7205
06:52:37.690 --> 06:52:40.770
he gets into the eternal abode of the Lord.

7206
06:52:41.830 --> 06:52:43.990
So, one of the services to the Lord

7207
06:52:43.990 --> 06:52:47.070
is preaching the common human values.

7208
06:52:47.330 --> 06:52:49.350
The eight foundations of the creative society

7209
06:52:49.350 --> 06:52:51.950
include what God Krishna

7210
06:52:51.950 --> 06:52:53.210
said in the Holy Scriptures.

7211
06:52:53.210 --> 06:52:55.230
It is on this foundation

7212
06:52:55.230 --> 06:52:57.170
that our world should stand,

7213
06:52:57.310 --> 06:52:58.810
but the modern society

7214
06:52:58.810 --> 06:53:00.030
is arranged differently.

7215
06:53:01.190 --> 06:53:03.290
It pulls a person down,

7216
06:53:03.450 --> 06:53:06.030
it doesn't inspire him to the spiritual path.

7217
06:53:06.190 --> 06:53:08.090
It's very difficult to remain spiritual

7218
06:53:08.090 --> 06:53:09.510
in such a world,

7219
06:53:09.750 --> 06:53:11.710
and every person just tries

7220
06:53:11.710 --> 06:53:15.170
to satisfy his endless material desires.

7221
06:53:15.330 --> 06:53:18.110
But God has given us freedom of choice

7222
06:53:18.110 --> 06:53:20.650
on which path we want to follow —

7223
06:53:20.650 --> 06:53:22.030
to turn away from Him

7224
06:53:22.030 --> 06:53:24.190
or to open our hearts

7225
06:53:24.190 --> 06:53:26.050
towards the creative society

7226
06:53:26.970 --> 06:53:29.210
that God himself

7227
06:53:29.210 --> 06:53:30.610
and our prophets spoke about.

7228
06:53:31.590 --> 06:53:34.230
As it is said in the Vedas,

7229
06:53:34.430 --> 06:53:37.770
if we take one small step towards Krishna,

7230
06:53:38.210 --> 06:53:41.430
He will take ten huge steps towards us.

7231
06:53:42.190 --> 06:53:44.390
So, let's not slow down

7232
06:53:44.390 --> 06:53:45.770
and let's make our choice

7233
06:53:45.770 --> 06:53:47.850
towards the creative society

7234
06:53:47.850 --> 06:53:51.050
and make our dreams of our prophets come true.

7235
06:53:51.050 --> 06:53:53.330
We are all children of God,

7236
06:53:53.570 --> 06:53:55.590
and we can compare Krishna

7237
06:53:55.590 --> 06:53:58.450
to a little drop

7238
06:53:58.450 --> 06:54:00.850
of the beautiful ocean.

7239
06:54:01.550 --> 06:54:02.270
Thank you very much,

7240
06:54:02.850 --> 06:54:03.590
Hare Krishna!

7241
06:54:04.030 --> 06:54:05.590
It is a great honor for me

7242
06:54:05.590 --> 06:54:08.370
to introduce our guest

7243
06:54:08.370 --> 06:54:10.390
who is famous in Russia

7244
06:54:10.390 --> 06:54:11.370
and in other countries.

7245
06:54:11.570 --> 06:54:13.910
He is a specialist in religion,

7246
06:54:14.730 --> 06:54:16.270
a philosopher,

7247
06:54:16.450 --> 06:54:19.050
Alexander Gennadievich Hakimov.

7248
06:54:19.830 --> 06:54:20.770
Dear friends,

7249
06:54:21.850 --> 06:54:23.650
accept my respect

7250
06:54:23.650 --> 06:54:24.810
and gratitude

7251
06:54:24.810 --> 06:54:28.410
for your good intentions

7252
06:54:29.050 --> 06:54:31.210
and for the pure motive

7253
06:54:31.210 --> 06:54:33.950
of the spiritualization of the society

7254
06:54:33.950 --> 06:54:36.430
that we should return

7255
06:54:36.550 --> 06:54:38.650
to the eternal values of the prophets.

7256
06:54:39.010 --> 06:54:40.730
My appeal is

7257
06:54:40.730 --> 06:54:45.510
that we should not wait

7258
06:54:45.510 --> 06:54:46.570
for new prophets

7259
06:54:46.570 --> 06:54:49.930
but should turn our faces

7260
06:54:49.930 --> 06:54:51.770
to the prophets

7261
06:54:51.770 --> 06:54:53.470
who have just come to us.

7262
06:54:55.050 --> 06:54:57.050
They are already prophets.

7263
06:54:57.850 --> 06:54:59.390
Christians have Jesus,

7264
06:55:00.690 --> 06:55:03.010
Muslims have Prophet Muhammad,

7265
06:55:04.470 --> 06:55:08.270
Gaudi Vaishnav has Shri Chaitanya Mahaprabhu,

7266
06:55:09.290 --> 06:55:11.090
Buddhists have Buddha.

7267
06:55:11.970 --> 06:55:13.050
Make your choice

7268
06:55:13.050 --> 06:55:14.070
and turn your faces

7269
06:55:14.070 --> 06:55:14.750
to the prophet.

7270
06:55:15.590 --> 06:55:16.550
Religion is not a religion.

7271
06:55:16.550 --> 06:55:17.130
There are many religions.

7272
06:55:17.330 --> 06:55:19.430
They can conflict with each other.

7273
06:55:19.690 --> 06:55:20.650
But prophets have never

7274
06:55:21.290 --> 06:55:21.850
conflicted with each other

7275
06:55:21.850 --> 06:55:22.490
in the past,

7276
06:55:22.890 --> 06:55:23.990
will not conflict today

7277
06:55:23.990 --> 06:55:24.970
and will not conflict in the future.

7278
06:55:26.870 --> 06:55:28.430
The point is that we turn

7279
06:55:28.430 --> 06:55:29.770
for some reason to confessions

7280
06:55:29.770 --> 06:55:30.450
and not to God.

7281
06:55:31.630 --> 06:55:33.190
We look at our confession

7282
06:55:33.190 --> 06:55:35.090
and begin to see the difference.

7283
06:55:35.770 --> 06:55:37.290
Let's turn to the prophets

7284
06:55:37.290 --> 06:55:38.990
and see that it turns out

7285
06:55:38.990 --> 06:55:40.350
that they talk about the same thing,

7286
06:55:40.790 --> 06:55:42.050
about care, love,

7287
06:55:43.230 --> 06:55:44.670
forgiveness, service,

7288
06:55:46.290 --> 06:55:47.290
about eliminating exploitation

7289
06:55:47.790 --> 06:55:48.890
of people by people.

7290
06:55:49.050 --> 06:55:50.310
Isn't that what it's all about?

7291
06:55:50.470 --> 06:55:52.130
All the prophets at the same time

7292
06:55:52.130 --> 06:55:54.050
from the same source.

7293
06:55:55.330 --> 06:55:56.550
And it is written in the Qur'an

7294
06:55:56.550 --> 06:55:58.490
that we sent you before

7295
06:55:58.490 --> 06:56:00.810
Moses, Jesus, Mary,

7296
06:56:01.190 --> 06:56:03.450
that is, Jesus, Moses, Mary.

7297
06:56:04.030 --> 06:56:05.010
One source

7298
06:56:05.010 --> 06:56:06.770
we sent to you.

7299
06:56:06.770 --> 06:56:09.450
And now we are sending

7300
06:56:09.450 --> 06:56:10.770
another prophet.

7301
06:56:10.970 --> 06:56:12.390
Look how many prophets there were.

7302
06:56:12.510 --> 06:56:14.110
Let's turn to the prophets

7303
06:56:14.110 --> 06:56:15.290
a little bit from our confessions.

7304
06:56:15.390 --> 06:56:16.050
Let's distance ourselves

7305
06:56:17.610 --> 06:56:19.510
from our climatic conditions

7306
06:56:20.290 --> 06:56:22.650
and turn to the spiritual side.

7307
06:56:22.770 --> 06:56:24.090
Because God is not a Muslim,

7308
06:56:24.470 --> 06:56:26.010
not a Christian, not a Hindu.

7309
06:56:26.790 --> 06:56:28.650
He is spiritual, absolutely spiritual.

7310
06:56:28.750 --> 06:56:30.610
He is the same for everyone as the sun.

7311
06:56:32.510 --> 06:56:34.010
It is a blessing for everyone

7312
06:56:34.010 --> 06:56:34.690
like the sun.

7313
06:56:34.690 --> 06:56:36.370
He is compared to the sun.

7314
06:56:36.530 --> 06:56:37.250
A good example.

7315
06:56:37.610 --> 06:56:39.650
This is exactly what my call is about.

7316
06:56:39.750 --> 06:56:41.670
That we turn to the prophets directly,

7317
06:56:41.970 --> 06:56:43.290
to their commandments and instructions.

7318
06:56:43.710 --> 06:56:44.570
Choose any.

7319
06:56:45.370 --> 06:56:45.830
There will be no harm.

7320
06:56:47.290 --> 06:56:48.670
But you need to follow,

7321
06:56:48.850 --> 06:56:50.370
not just call yourself a Christian,

7322
06:56:50.650 --> 06:56:51.990
a Muslim or a Krishnaite,

7323
06:56:52.450 --> 06:56:53.410
but you need to follow

7324
06:56:53.410 --> 06:56:56.230
what our spiritual leaders say,

7325
06:56:57.370 --> 06:56:58.130
the leaders of the world,

7326
06:56:58.750 --> 06:56:59.490
the great souls.

7327
06:57:00.430 --> 06:57:02.510
Then the world will undoubtedly change.

7328
06:57:03.770 --> 06:57:05.490
And of course I expect

7329
06:57:05.490 --> 06:57:07.390
that we will actually be

7330
06:57:07.390 --> 06:57:08.470
a very useful society

7331
06:57:08.470 --> 06:57:09.090
for the whole world.

7332
06:57:10.230 --> 06:57:12.570
The creation of a single spiritual culture

7333
06:57:12.570 --> 06:57:14.210
uniting the society of people

7334
06:57:14.210 --> 06:57:16.170
establishing peace,

7335
06:57:16.890 --> 06:57:18.130
care, love

7336
06:57:18.130 --> 06:57:20.270
for the neighbor, love for God,

7337
06:57:20.390 --> 06:57:21.410
love for nature.

7338
06:57:22.850 --> 06:57:24.510
And many other values

7339
06:57:24.510 --> 06:57:25.570
will undoubtedly awaken

7340
06:57:26.450 --> 06:57:28.190
when we come into contact with God.

7341
06:57:28.850 --> 06:57:31.270
Maybe we will have time

7342
06:57:31.270 --> 06:57:33.930
to live in this divine culture.

7343
06:57:35.150 --> 06:57:36.830
That's why I wish everyone

7344
06:57:36.830 --> 06:57:39.250
on this path of development

7345
06:57:39.250 --> 06:57:40.610
and great success.

7346
06:57:41.290 --> 06:57:42.450
Thank you very much.

7347
06:57:46.140 --> 06:57:47.560
Thank you very much.

7348
06:57:48.020 --> 06:57:48.900
Thank you so much.

7349
06:57:49.460 --> 06:57:51.700
Thank you so much.

