06:57:51.700 --> 06:57:53.000
Now it's a great pleasure

7351
06:57:54.280 --> 06:57:55.340
for me to introduce

7352
06:57:55.340 --> 06:57:56.600
to you our speaker

7353
06:57:56.600 --> 06:57:58.240
Dr. Chintamani Yogi

7354
06:57:58.240 --> 06:57:59.860
who is a researcher

7355
06:57:59.860 --> 06:58:02.780
of Nepal, a thinker, a philosopher,

7356
06:58:03.040 --> 06:58:04.440
a spiritual master, a teacher,

7357
06:58:04.900 --> 06:58:06.120
an activist of the world,

7358
06:58:06.300 --> 06:58:08.120
the founder of the Hindu school

7359
06:58:08.840 --> 06:58:09.140
Vidyayogi.

7360
06:58:09.320 --> 06:58:10.640
Please, the floor is yours.

7361
06:58:13.010 --> 06:58:17.730
I would like to pay my very high respect

7362
06:58:17.730 --> 06:58:19.370
to all the great scriptures

7363
06:58:19.370 --> 06:58:21.130
and great prophets of the world.

7364
06:58:21.610 --> 06:58:23.710
Being a Hindu, I feel happy

7365
06:58:23.710 --> 06:58:25.190
to also respect the Bible,

7366
06:58:25.630 --> 06:58:27.850
the Koran, the Tripitaka,

7367
06:58:29.470 --> 06:58:31.090
the Agama Sutras,

7368
06:58:31.090 --> 06:58:32.810
and Guru Granth Sahib.

7369
06:58:34.750 --> 06:58:36.210
That's what makes me a Hindu.

7370
