If I deny someone's existence,

7372
06:58:44.510 --> 06:58:45.370
someone's history,

7373
06:58:45.730 --> 06:58:47.070
someone's serious contribution

7374
06:58:48.870 --> 06:58:50.550
to the human society,

7375
06:58:50.570 --> 06:58:52.070
