7376
06:58:53.210 --> 06:58:53.890
I'm not a Hindu.

7377
06:58:55.110 --> 06:58:56.200
So that's what I request,

7378
06:58:56.890 --> 06:58:57.430
first of all.

7379
06:58:57.650 --> 06:58:59.170
My primary wish

