I said, no, I don't know.

7395
06:59:34.290 --> 06:59:34.950
I don't know.

7396
06:59:35.090 --> 06:59:36.630
I'm a teacher of yoga.

7397
06:59:37.230 --> 06:59:38.310
I'm a spiritual seeker.

7398
06:59:39.050 --> 06:59:40.230
I'm a teacher of Hinduism,

7399
06:59:41.230 --> 06:59:41.830
a philosopher.

7400
06:59:42.150 --> 06:59:44.270
But I don't know how many gods and goddesses,

7401
06:59:44.330 --> 06:59:45.210
how many holy books, scriptures,

7402
06:59:45.690 --> 06:59:46.790
how many traditions,

7403
