07:00:01.250 --> 07:00:03.790
There are many wonderful messages.

7409
07:00:03.910 --> 07:00:06.050
And these messages

7410
07:00:06.050 --> 07:00:08.190
perfectly support the concept

7411
07:00:08.690 --> 07:00:10.910
of the creative society.

7412
07:00:10.950 --> 07:00:14.630
Society must be creative

7413
07:00:14.630 --> 07:00:17.430
with very unconditional love

7414
07:00:17.430 --> 07:00:19.050
for human beings.

7415
07:00:19.170 --> 07:00:20.210
Society must be creative

7416
07:00:20.210 --> 07:00:21.930
with unconditional love

7417
07:00:21.950 --> 07:00:23.250
for human beings.

7418
07:00:23.250 --> 07:00:23.730
with equal respect

7419
07:00:23.730 --> 07:00:26.050
for human beings

7420
07:00:26.050 --> 07:00:28.290
and for any other being.

